Introduction

Rendezvous (Korean: 랑데뷰) was a girl group formed by Parksal Entertainment. On August 7, 2019, they released a pre-debebut single titled “Summer Paradise”. The group currently consists of four members: Suri, Seulgi, Lingyi, and Seunghee.

The group had planned to release their debut single “Q” in November 2019, but the group was announced to have disbanded on December 6, 2019. Three out of the four members opened up personal Instagram accounts and Lingyi announced that she was ready for a new beginning in early November.

Parksal Entertainment said that they would concentrate on the sole remaining member, Seulgi, and launch her as a soloist.
